name: THE ARGENTINIAN
description: June 22nd. 1986. Buenos Aires. Argentina was playing one of the most important soccer matches in history vs England. Laura was about to have her first child. She knew it was a boy, but the name was not decided yet. The match started, and a man called Diego made the best goal ever. “I’ll call him Diego” said Laura. Nowadays, Diego has three passions: Soccer, Mate, and Asado.
